txt.en: The Regmyl in Nargroth serve Borangos the Horror. Their presence shows the power that Borangos holds over the caverns of fire. You should defeat any Regmyl you come across and destroy the shrines they worship.
Nargroth is located in Talath Úrui.\n\nYou should defeat Regmyl and destroy shrines to Borangos.
Defeated many Regmyl and destroyed shrines to Borangos.
Nargroth is located in Talath Úrui.\n\nYou should defeat Regmyl and destroy shrines to Borangos.
Nargroth, the caverns of fire, is home to many creatures of flame.
You have successfully defeated many Regmyl and destroyed shrines to Borangos within the fire caverns of Nargroth. Your efforts should slowly weaken the hold that Borangos has over Talath Úrui.
